
Local variables stored in Stack
Global variables stored in blocks adjacend to:	rw-p / r--p

Non-static variables stored in the Heap

VVAR	---->	 Stores all the basic functions a program may need such as cpuinfo or gettimeofday	

Permissions:
	r	-->	Read
	w	-->	Write
	x	-->	Execute
	
	p	-->	
	
	First triplet	---->	User permissions
	Secnd triplet	---->	User group permissions
	Thrd  triplet	---->	Others permissions